{
  "stem": "22047.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you try to figure out from what direction this round is coming, and you go to the opposite side of the tree.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And unless it hits in the top of this tree that you're behind, you're-- you're probably going to survive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so there was a lot of skirmishes in this area, in Hagenow and Schweighausen and some of those small towns.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We-- as a matter of fact, in this area, we had-- we had been forced back again.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were in an outpost line across this open valley.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we pulled back after we were contacted by the Germans, pulled back across this valley.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the regimental commander wanted us to go back out and re-assume the-- the positions we were in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And our company commander fought this, because he said they're already there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, I don't care.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You send your troops back out there and retake that position.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was Colonel Luongo.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, we went-- we almost got back to where the positions were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was out in the front of my platoon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I looked up, and here's some binoculars looking at me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so I said, Krauts!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we spread out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I-- I ended up in a mine field-- anti-tank minefield.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the people back on the main line saw what was going on, so they called in artillery to fire on the Germans that were right there and right out in front of me, not 50 yards.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And some of this artillery was-- was landing in the minefield that I was lying in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I could look up, and I could see-- [LAUGHS] see Germans, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I-- I tried to-- to make myself as small as possible.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
